added.title: Monster in the Garden
added.description: Craig is determined to catch the monster that has been wreaking havoc in Granddad's garden.

added.title: The Curse
added.description: Craig, Kelsey and JP run afoul of some no-good teenage witches and are cursed! Lousy teenagers!

added.title: Dog Decider
added.description: Unable to make tough decisions, Craig decides to put his choices in the hands of a dog named Fred.

added.title: Bring Out Your Beast
added.description: Craig wants to play a popular card game, so he decides to borrow Bernard's vintage and valuable cards.

added.title: Lost in the Sewer
added.description: Craig agrees to help The Sewer Queen map the sewers, but he quickly finds himself in over his head.

added.title: Balloon Boys
added.description: Vic & Val go on a hot air balloon trip with Sal and compete to be his favorite, but things go awry when they try to use the magical Nazca Lines to their advantage.

added.title: Escape From Bebe Bay
added.description: When Vic & Val accidentally turn themselves and Don into babies, they must escape a daycare center in order to change back to their normal ages.

added.title: #ShockItToMe
added.description: Leslie Willis, the meanest girl in school, becomes a social media sensation by posting mean-spirited videos on her MetropoVids channel, causing Wonder Woman to question the moral integrity of the people who live in the World of Man.

added.title: #SheMightBeGiant
added.description: Karen Beecher is always getting picked on at school, but when the local mall is attacked by a monstrous supervillain called Giganta, she discovers that tiny Bumblebee might be the only one small enough to save the day.

added.title: #FightAtTheMuseum
added.description: Supergirl always relies on her strength, but she'll need more than brawn to stop brainy Catwoman from stealing valuable gems from the local science museum.

added.title: #FromBatToWorse
added.description: Having just moved to the boring Metropolis suburbs, Batgirl is thrilled when she intercepts a call from Batman asking for help. But before she can stop a visiting Gotham villain, she'll have to sneak past her dad, Police Commissioner Gordon.

added.title: #CrushingIt
added.description: Diana Prince is absolutely crushing it in every single aspect of life as a student at Metropolis High, until someone shows up who threatens to throw her off her game for good.

added.title: Idiosyncratic Induction
added.description: On Elliott's first day at the Hive, he meets the most unusual characters on his adventure so far.

added.title: Memory Mayhem
added.description: Frankie tries to discover more about the mysterious rock that bought them to their new home, with the help of an entity called The Head.

added.title: Claudus
added.description: Lion-O's dad King Claudus arrives on Third Earth, and turns out to be a big selfish jerk! Now Lion-O has to deal with his dad before he goes to war with the rest of the Thundercats.

added.title: Telethon
added.description: In order to save the Berbils, Cheetara uses her psychic powers to project a telethon into the brains of everyone on Third Earth.

added.title: Mall-Ra
added.description: Mumm-Ra builds a mall that's actually a giant labyrinth designed to trap the Thundercats forever. Too bad the Thundercats love the mall so much they could literally spend all eternity there.

added.title: Eclipsorr
added.description: Third Earth's sun is being blocked out by the Eclipsor Corporation, an amoral company that wants to sell its energy for a profit. The ThunderCats can't do anything about it because they don't have a spaceship, yet!

added.title: Wizz-Ra
added.description: The ThunderCats freak out when a spooky ghost dressed like a pharaoh appears in their mirrors! They quickly set about to getting rid of every reflective surface in their lair, because that ghost is scary and no one wants to talk to him!

added.title: Never Trust a Human
added.description: A flashback episode tells the story of Young Wu and Young Garmadon meeting Aspheera and teaching her the secrets of Spinjitzu.

added.title: Under Siege
added.description: Having learned Master Wu is the "Treacherous One," the ninja find themselves under siege at the Monastery, trying to protect Wu from the wrath of Aspheera.

added.title: The Explorer's Club
added.description: The ninja must break into the Explorer's Club to obtain the second Scroll of Forbidden Spinjitzu, running afoul of the club's manager and irate club-members.

added.title: Vengeance Is Mine!
added.description: Aspheera arrives at the Monastery of Spinjitzu and confronts Wu, forcing one of the ninja to make a heroic sacrifice.

added.title: A Cold Goodbye
added.description: Having learned Zane is not dead, Master Wu prepares to go after him, but Lloyd and the other ninja take matters into their own hands and defy their Master.

added.title: Guidance
added.description: Amethyst has been helping Little Homeschool Gems find jobs on the boardwalk, but Steven isn't sure about her approach.

added.title: Rose Buds
added.description: Steven gets a surprise visit from some old friends, and an even more surprising introduction to some new ones.

added.title: Opposites Attract
added.description: Claiming he's good at heart, Dynamo convinces Axel and the team to help him find a battery that can power his centrifuge and free him from Madtrap's control - but Bobbie Blobby isn't buying the baddie's story.

added.title: The Thing in the Wall
added.description: When Axel and the team accuse Galileo of stealing their possessions, the lizard must hunt down the true culprit - a mysterious creature behind the wall - to prove his innocence.

added.title: Madtrap
added.description: Madcap and Princess SugarSalt trap Axel and the team inside a Minergy-powered labyrinth that attacks them with their greatest fears, forcing them to work together and escape as a unit.

added.title: To Tame the Perilous Skies!
added.description: With Axel's drone-wing broken, the team must find another way to stop Madcap and his minions as they take to the skies in toy airplanes for an aerial assault on the city park.

added.title: Four Color Fallout
added.description: Axel, Galileo, and Sarge get Minergy-transported by Madcap into the pages of Axel's favorite comic book, the hero of which turns out not to be so cool after all.

added.title: Origin of Species
added.description: Origin of Species, Part 1: Dan meets his partner Bakugan Drago for the first time and we learn about the incident that happened on Earth twelve years ago./Origin of Species, Part 2: Dan and friends win the Bakugan Battle, firmly establishing the Awesome Ones as our heroes and Bakugan Brawlers.

added.title: Burger Run/Monkey See, Monkey Don't
added.description: Burger Run: When the local Burger Joint is being threatened by a rogue Bakugan, Dan steps up to save the day and the burgers!/Monkey See, Monkey Don't: The AO stop neighborhood kids from copycat behavior (namely, using their Bakugan for frivolous reasons).

added.title: Bully for You/Trolling for Laughs
added.description: Bully for You: The AO must handle a neighborhood bully who is using his Bakugan to pick on the local kids./Trolling for Laughs: Wynton's constant practical jokes wear thin on his Bakugan Trox so the Bakugan decide to teach him a lesson.

added.title: Local Heroes/Pegatrix
added.description: Local Heroes: After the AO cause accidental destruction Dan's parents question whether the kids should be allowed to keep their Bakugan./Pegatrix: Lia disagrees with her new Bakugan Pegatrix on battle techniques but during a fierce fight Lia must rely on Pegatrix's battle savy.

added.title: Frenemies/Strata's Fear
added.description: Frenemies: Two new Bakugan Brawlers, Shun and Magnus, try out for the AO./Strata's Fear: The AO solve the mystery of a kid's missing Bakugan and meet a Bakugan Hunter named Strata.

added.title: Thumb War
added.description: The gang decide to compete in the annual Thumb War competition, but a surprise forces Mao Mao to deal with the unthinkable... losing.

added.title: All By Mao Self
added.description: Mao Mao's desire to be a legend drives him to keep topping himself. But how much is enough?

added.title: He's the Sheriff
added.description: The gang struggles to get rid of the King when he joins them as their new deputy-for-a-day!

added.title: Bobo Chan
added.description: Badgerclops adopts an abandoned monster, but some things are better left in the wild.

added.title: Small
added.description: Mao Mao's legendary, gigantic and critical father visits his son at his new job as sheriff.

added.title: Ninos de Globo
added.description: Vic y Val salen de viaje en globo aerostático con Sal y compiten por ser su favorito, pero las cosas se complican cuando tratan de usar las mágicas líneas de Nazca a su favor.

added.title: El Gran Robo de Bongos
added.description: Los chicos olvidan conseguir un regalo para Chata en el Día de la Abuela y en un movimiento desesperado, le regalan los bongos que pidieron prestados a Xochi. Sabiendo que deben devolver los tambores, Victor y Valentino fingen ser ladrones para robar los instrumentos.

added.title: Escape de Bahia Bebe
added.description: Cuando, por accidente, Vic y Val se convierten a sí mismos y a Don en bebés, deben escapar de una guardería para poder volver a sus edades normales.

added.title: Consejos
added.description: Amatista ha estado ayudando a las Gemas de Pequeña Escuela Madre a encontrar trabajo, pero Steven no está seguro de su enfoque.

added.title: Capullos de Rosa
added.description: Steven recibe una visita sorpresa de algunos viejos amigos y una introducción aún más sorprendente a algunos nuevos.

added.title: Monstruo en el Jardin
added.description: Craig está decidido a atrapar al monstruo que ha estado desatando un caos en el jardín del abuelo.
added.originalseriesname: Craig of the Creek en Espanol

added.title: La Maldicion
added.description: Craig, Kelsey y JP entran en conflicto con unas brujas adolescentes deshonestas, ique les lanzan una maldición! iQué adolescentes malvadas!
added.originalseriesname: Craig of the Creek en Espanol

added.title: #CortoCircuito
added.description: Leslie Willis, la chica mas cruel de la escuela, se convierte en una sensación de las redes sociales al subir videos malintencionados a su canal, haciendo que Wonder Woman cuestione la integridad moral de quienes viven en el Mundo del Hombre.
added.originalseriesname: DC Super Hero Girls en Espanol

added.title: Perro Decisivo
added.description: Incapaz de tomar decisiones difíciles, Craig decide poner sus decisiones en manos de un perro llamado Fred.
added.originalseriesname: Craig of the Creek en Espanol

added.title: Jamas Confies en un Humano
added.description: Mientras Aspheera busca vengarse del "Engañador Traicionero" que la traicionó, el ninja hace un sorprendente descubrimiento.

added.title: Saca tu Bestia
added.description: Craig quiere jugar a un popular juego de cartas, así que decide tomar prestadas las cartas antiguas y valiosas de Bernard.
added.originalseriesname: Craig of the Creek en Espanol

added.title: #AunqueSeaGigante
added.description: Karen Beecher siempre es molestada en la escuela. Pero cuando el centro comercial es atacado por una monstruosa super villana llamada Giganta, Karen descubre que la diminuta Bumblebee puede ser la única suficientemente pequeña para salvar el día.
added.originalseriesname: DC Super Hero Girls en Espanol

added.title: Sitiados
added.description: Habiendo aprendido que el Maestro Wu es el "Traicionero", los ninja se encuentran asediados en el Monasterio, tratando de proteger a Wu de la ira de Aspheera.

added.title: Lucha de Pulgares
added.description: El trío decide concursar en la competencia anual de Lucha de Pulgares, pero una sorpresa obliga a Mao Mao a lidiar con algo impensado… la derrota.

added.title: #BatallaEnElMuseo
added.description: Supergirl siempre confía en su fuerza, pero necesitará mas que músculos para impedir que la astuta Catwoman robe unas valiosas gemas del museo de ciencias.
added.originalseriesname: DC Super Hero Girls en Espanol

added.title: El Club de Exploradores
added.description: El ninja debe entrar en el Club del Explorador para obtener el segundo Pergamino de Spinjitzu Prohibido, en conflicto con el gerente del club y los miembros furiosos del club.

added.title: Perdidos en la Cloaca
added.description: Craig acepta ayudar a la Reina de las Alcantarillas a trazar el mapa de las alcantarillas, pero rápidamente se encuentra en una situación que lo supera.
added.originalseriesname: Craig of the Creek en Espanol

added.title: La Venganza es Mia
added.description: Aspheera llega al Monasterio de Spinjitzu y se enfrenta a Wu, obligando a uno de los ninjas a hacer un sacrificio heroico.

added.title: Todo Por Mao Mismo
added.description: El deseo de Mao Mao de convertirse en leyenda lo lleva a querer superarse a sí mismo una y otra vez. ¿Pero cuánto es suficiente?

added.title: #DeMalEnPeor
added.description: Habiéndose mudado a los aburridos suburbios de Metrópolis, Batgirl se emociona cuando intercepta una llamada de auxilio de Batman. Pero antes de que pueda ir a detener a un villano visitante de Ciudad Gótica, Barbara debe escabullirse de su casa y de su padre, el comisionado Gordon.
added.originalseriesname: DC Super Hero Girls en Espanol

added.title: El es el Sheriff
added.description: iEl trío lucha por deshacerse del Rey cuando los acompaña como nuevo ayudante del sheriff por un día!

added.title: Una Fria Despedida
added.description: Habiendo aprendido que Zane no está muerto, el Maestro Wu se prepara para ir tras él, pero Lloyd y el otro ninja toman el asunto en sus propias manos y desafían a su Maestro.

added.title: #ElFlechazo
added.description: Diana Prince está triunfando en todos los aspectos de la vida y como alumna de la Secundaria Metrópolis... hasta que alguien llega para confundirla totalmente.
added.originalseriesname: DC Super Hero Girls en Espanol

added.title: Bobo Chan
added.description: Colosal adopta a un monstruo abandonado, pero es mejor dejar algunas cosas en estado salvaje.

added.title: Pequeno
added.description: El legendario, gigantesco y crítico padre de Mao Mao visita a su hijo en su nuevo trabajo como sheriff.

added.title: La Cosa en la Pared
added.description: Cuando Axel y el equipo acusan a Galileo de robar sus posesiones, el lagarto debe cazar al verdadero culpable, una misteriosa criatura detrás del muro, para demostrar su inocencia.

added.title: La Trampa de Madcap
added.description: Madcap y Princess SugarSalt atrapan a Axel y al equipo dentro de un laberinto impulsado por Minergy que los ataca con sus mayores temores, obligándolos a trabajar juntos y escapar como una unidad.

added.title: A Domar Los Cielos Peligrosos
added.description: Con el ala del avión no tripulado de Axel roto, el equipo debe encontrar otra forma de detener a Madcap y sus secuaces mientras se lanzan a los cielos en aviones de juguete para un asalto aéreo en el parque de la ciudad.

added.title: Efectos en Cuatro Colores
added.description: Axel, Galileo y Sarge son transportados por Minergy por Madcap a las páginas del cómic favorito de Axel, cuyo héroe resulta no ser tan genial después de todo.

added.title: Sonrie y Aguanta
added.description: Cuando un dolor de muelas envía a Axel al dentista, el equipo debe luchar contra la Princesa SugarSalt, quien confunde la nueva "corona" de Axel con la realidad.

added.title: Bromas Pesadas
added.description: Las constantes bromas pesadas de Wynton colman la paciencia de su Bakugan, Trox, quien decide darle una lección.

added.title: Una Leccion para Todos
added.description: Los Fantásticos le enseñan a unos chicos del vecindario a no imitar a los demás. Por ejemplo, a quienes utilizan a sus Bakugan con fines frívolos.

added.title: El Bravucon
added.description: Los Fantásticos deben lidiar con un bravucón que usa a su Bakugan para intimidar a los chicos del vecindario.

added.title: El Origen de las Especies Parte 2
added.description: Dan y sus amigos ganan la Batalla Bakugan, demostrando que los Fantásticos son nuestros héroes y los mejores Peleadores Bakugan.

added.title: Pegatrix
added.description: Lia no concuerda con las técnicas de Pegatrix, pero durante una intensa batalla, debe aprender a confiar en los conocimientos de su Bakugan.

added.title: El Origen de las Especies Parte 1
added.description: Dan conoce a su pareja Bakugan, Drago, por primera vez y nos enteramos del "incidente" que ocurrió en la Tierra hace doce años.

added.title: Heroes Locales
added.description: Los Fantásticos provocan una ola de destrucción por accidente, y los padres de Dan se preguntan si deberían permitirle a los niños conservar sus Bakugan.

added.title: Un Almuerzo Inesperado
added.description: Cuando el Restaurante de Hamburguesas es amenazado por un violento Bakugan, Dan llega para salvar el día...y las hamburguesas.

added.title: El Miedo de Strata
added.description: Los Fantásticos resuelven la misteriosa desaparición del Bakugan de un niño, y conocen a un cazador de Bakugan llamado Strata.

added.title: Ene-Amigos
added.description: Dos nuevos Peleadores Bakugan, Shun y Magnus, buscan ser parte de Los Fantásticos.
